"Hatiku bergoyang... Bergoyang..."

00:09:06.080 --> 00:09:13.240
"Hatiku bergoyang... Bergoyang..."

00:09:13.640 --> 00:09:21.120
"Seperti malaikat,
malaikat, ia melihatmu."

